Ribby's obsession with Lappy intensified, as did his worries for her
and the worn-out laptop. Lappy's once-bright screen had darkened,
and its overworked processor was struggling to keep up with Ribby's 
demands. Concerned for Ribby's safety, her relatives and friends interfered,
persuading her to venture outside her room. Ribby needed to develop new interests
and give Lappy the relaxation she needed, fostering a healthier balance in her life.
